  "description": "Franco 'Bifo' Berardi (1949–) is an Italian autonomist Marxist whose work on semiocapitalism, the soul at work, and the conditions of cognitive labor under platformal capitalism develops a sustained phenomenology of the late-capitalist subject's affective and somatic exhaustion.",
